_sText:
Hey guys,
This map was one of those that I started out with random thoughts and just threw them together, all in all i think it turned out good for that reason. It has a basement, two water pools at each base, a second floor, and a sniper tower for each base. There are 24 spawn points (I know, not 32, that would be way to many players for this map though.)

I hope you guys like it.

Version 2 is out, please check out this link if you want the updates.
http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/69250
